{"tid":783273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[700及藍籌者福音] 觀塘小店發起飯券募捐　中秋節長者不用再食二手飯","createTime":"2018-08-17T11:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T15:11:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"742bd2c8f21953dfad255eab2d56de40e03c33cd","tid":783273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1759947/org/35e6f8962b9f8b4689d14a4f9a653680.jpeg/RLZIoIAIZRIeih3KQtKjNkRTiZ_7zpt7OYmZfzmJmX8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1759947%2Forg%2F35e6f8962b9f8b4689d14a4f9a653680.jpeg%2FRLZIoIAIZRIeih3KQtKjNkRTiZ_7zpt7OYmZfzmJmX8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=90c973de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中秋節下月就到，但清貧及獨居長者卻未必享受到「人月兩團圓」。有餐廳小店與慈善團體合作，今日發起飯券募捐活動，計劃製作「長者中秋膳心飯盒」，於中秋節當日向觀塘2000位清貧長者免費派發，讓他們「不用再食二手飯」，感受人間溫暖，亦冀透過送暖活動喚醒市民關心長者需要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/224069/人月兩團圓-觀塘小店發起飯券募捐-中秋節長者不用再食二手飯\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F224069%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A9%E5%9C%98%E5%9C%93-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%A3%AF%E5%88%B8%E5%8B%9F%E6%8D%90-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E7%AF%80%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%86%8D%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E9%A3%AF&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2Rykb7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d38e7797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/224069/人月兩團圓-觀塘小店發起飯券募捐-中秋節長者不用再食二手飯</a>"},{"pid":"77f7d8cd9e4fd42b0b1c2ecef19e4df6c98f28de","tid":783273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe02d30d434f38e48f06916575aaf9c22233a55","tid":783273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc